data.description: *** Buyers can save money! Home Qualifies for Loan Assumption (3.25% Int rate) *** This is a well-maintained and move-in-ready 3-level Townhome nestled within the coveted Wetherbrooke gated community, just 5 miles from The Battery and I-285/I-75. Though minutes from major highways, you're still off the beaten path to create a serene place to come home to every day. This spacious 4 bed 3.5 bath home welcomes you with a grand foyer, tray ceilings, exquisite, real hardwood floors throughout, and lots of natural light. Oversized primary bedroom with customized built-in, walk-in closet. The kitchen offers ample cabinetry with a view of the family room, making entertaining easy. Just off the family room is a sizable, private deck; the perfect oasis to enjoy your evenings after a long day! Large 12-seat dining room with adjacent flex space to fit your needs for extra entertaining or office space. Your 3rd level is complete with a separate bedroom and full bath with an open area for extra entertainment, fitness, office space, or whatever suits your needs. Near Silver Comet Trail, Truist Park Stadium (The Battery), Shopping, Restaurants and much more. Don't let this be the one that got away!
